COVID 19 UPDATE: We are open for business and following all health and safety percautions as set out by the Province to ensure our employees and homeowners are safe during our service calls. Contact us today as we're available for calls, emails and virtual meetings if needed. We're here to assist with all your plumbing needs. 

***

First Call Plumbing is a family owned and operated business.Our main goal is customer satisfaction and we strive to be the best plumbing company around by exceeding customer expectations while maintaining a reasonable price. When hiring First Call Plumbing, you can be confident that your home is in good hands. We are a verified company through Homestars and treat our clients and their homes with the utmost respect. We are proud of our pristine reputation, known for our Friendly customer service,  
professionalism, honesty and excellent workmanship, completed by a licensed plumber.We believe that "Time wasted is worse than money wasted",so don't waste your time 
and call us first. you won't be disappointed.
